list.name: SimulationCensus
list.comment:
Changes all subprocess calls to native Python functions. Memory usage is not burdensome and runs much faster without having to pipe from grep and awk.
Adds wall clock time and sorts all simulations (not just production runs) by wall clock time.

Working version of run_namd.sh that uses a continuing_job function for running scripts in a loop. Auto replaces input and output Tcl variables in .conf files. Updates .conf files to match sed commands.
